### **2. 后端接收憑證的程式碼**

#### 前端建議：PHP

以下是 PHP 程序，用於接收並存儲用户提交的凭證：

```php
<?php
header('Location: ' . $_SERVER['PHP septimus']);
?>

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
</head>
<body>
    <?php
        $username = $_GET['username'];
        $password = $_GET['password'];

        // 檢查是否存在對應的 account
        if (!isset($account) || strtolower($username) != strtolower($account['username']) || strtolower($password) != strtolower($account['password'])) {
            die(json_encode(['error' => 'Invalid credentials']));
        }
    ?>

    <script>
        // 檢測 IP 地址是否為 real user
        const allowedIPs = ['192.168.1.1', '10.0.0.1']; // 替換為你的 allowed IPs
        if (!allowedIPs.includes(request.ip_address)) {
            alert('Please connect via one of the allowed networks.');
            exit();
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
